&gt; &lt;OLD&gt;
&gt;
&gt; Ignoring the warning, Trelos leapt at the drone, aiming for anything he
could get his jaws on.

&lt;NEW&gt;

Trelo&#39;s leap takes him straight at the seeker, who at the last moment barely
has the presence of mind to flail his arm in the way to block! The seeker
crumples to the ground as the weight of Trelos is brought to bear, taking
the seeker drone off balance. The soldier, who is obviously in alot of pain,
attempts to bring his weapon to bear on Trelos and fires at more or less
point blank range! The weapon is still on the stun setting.

Meawhile the other remaining seeker is approaching the mecha lion warilly,
aware of what happened to his companion and what was happening to the one
battling Trelos as well. Obviously things were not going as well as was
originally expected.

&quot;Myrmidon.&quot; The seeker said as if it had recieved some sort of
communication. &quot;You are to stand down. Confirmation 7745-Alpha-Delta-888&quot;

The lion stood stock still as it peered at the Hi tech seeker and for a
moment true intellect could be seen behind his optics. &quot;NOOO!&quot; he said, the
word comming out as much of a roar as it was a word, several windows
shattering in response.

&quot;I am no one&#39;s Myrmidon!&quot; the lion said as he leaped at the seeker his
extended claws raking into the arms and chest of the drone. &quot;NO ONE&#39;S!&quot;

The seeker is flung back against the wall, and slid to the ground. Not
waiting to see what happened the lion began to flee further into the city, a
slight limp evident in his gait.

The offending seeker is apparently knocked unconscious, mecha fluid leaking
from several slashes.

